### =========================
### GET /me（正常）
### =========================
GET http://localhost:3000/api/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### GET /me（トークンなし）
GET http://localhost:3000/api/me

### GET /me（不正トークン）
GET http://localhost:3000/api/me
Authorization: Bearer invalid-token

### =========================
### GET /me/reservatoins (予約一覧取得)
### =========================
GET http://localhost:3000/api/me/reservations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### =========================
### PATCH /me（正常）
### =========================
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/me
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Updated User",
  "prefecture": "東京都"
}

### PATCH /me（email変更）
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/me
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "email": "new@example.com"
}

### PATCH /me（email形式エラー）
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/me
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "email": "invalid-email"
}

### PATCH /me（email重複）
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/me
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "email": "ouble@example.com"
}

### PATCH /me（データなし）
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/me
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{}